visualeditor-welcomedialog-content: Konyan maai jhyuk, a̱ghwon kuzang jhyi ni̱ beang.
visualeditor-welcomedialog-content-thank: Zi̱ gwai ma̱ng si̱sak nang a beang ta̱cya̱ ka ka̱ lyen nkyang njhyang!
